 3018        public string Getdisplaytext(string sConceptcodes, string sDomaincode)
 3019        {
 03020            iSOFT.LORENZO.Common.Framework.APPActivity objAppActivity = new APPActivity();
 03021            ReferenceCollection oRefcollection = new ReferenceCollection();
 03022            oRefcollection = objAppActivity.GetRefrenceCollection(sDomaincode);
 03023            string sTerm = string.Empty;
 03024             if (sConceptcodes != null && sConceptcodes.Length > 0)
 3025            {
 03026                string[] arrConceptCode = sConceptcodes.Split(','); //Array of rules
 03027                int nRuleCount = arrConceptCode.Length; //Count of rules
 03028                 for (int nCount = 0; nCount < nRuleCount; nCount++)
 3029                {
 03030                     if (oRefcollection[arrConceptCode[nCount]] != null)
 3031                    {
 03032                         if (nCount != nRuleCount - 1)
 03033                            sTerm = sTerm + oRefcollection[arrConceptCode[nCount]].DisplayName + ",";
 3034                        else
 03035                            sTerm = sTerm + oRefcollection[arrConceptCode[nCount]].DisplayName;
 3036                    }
 3037                }
 03038                return sTerm;
 3039            }
 3040            else
 03041                return sTerm;
 3042        }
